{"tid":2144849,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PlayStation 宣布跟進抵制仇恨不實言論 停止在 Facebook 上的一切廣告與活動","createTime":"2020-08-07T18:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T07:39:18.000Z","uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46e53b1278c680b8089da4cc03cbc1546c482208","tid":2144849,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T18:44:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=199500\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fgnn%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D199500&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6Bx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=84efeea3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=199500</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">唔怪得個page成個月冇更新</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS42020-07-03 18:04<br />\nPlayStation 宣布跟進抵制仇恨不實言論 停止在 Facebook 上的一切廣告與活動<br />\n&nbsp;（GNN 記者 Sam 報導）<br />\n<br />\n　　根據外媒報導，Sony 宣布將跟進福特汽車、可口可樂、惠普、星巴克、愛迪達等跨國企業的腳步，停止在 Facebook 與 Instagram 投放 PlayStation 的廣告，以抵制 Facebook 對仇恨與不實言論的消極態度。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n　　由於自 5 月美國黑人男性喬治‧佛洛伊德因警方過度執法身亡而爆發大規模抗議浪潮之後，Facebook&nbsp;並未如其他 SNS 平台如 Twitter 般調整其管理規範，仍允許發布仇恨與不實言論，因而遭到許多公民團體抗議。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n　　後續有六大非營利組織發起「#停止以仇恨牟利（#StopHateForProfit）」活動，呼籲各大廣告主停止對 Facebook 投放廣告，來迫使 Facebook 調整政策。該活動發起後，陸續獲得包括福特汽車、可口可樂、百事可樂、惠普、星巴克、愛迪達等跨國大企業的支持。如今 Sony 也宣布將響應此一活動，停止所有 PlayStation 品牌在 Facebook 與 Instagram 上的活動，包括付費廣告與非付費內容如粉絲團貼文，持續到 7 月底止。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n　　而日前才剛宣布結束直播平台 Mixer 服務、轉與 Facebook Gaming 深度合作的微軟，同樣也宣布將暫停在 Facebook 與 Instagram 投放廣告，同時強調合作並不代表 Facebook 廣告會在 Xbox&nbsp;儀表板上出現。"},{"pid":"6bbb40c7758cbc35d6b3c067907106ae17ada412","tid":2144849,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T18:49:51.000Z","msg":"最新一個po係六月<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XVuxNcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXVuxNcz.jpg&h=c886cba7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de27ee4e1a72228165fb140e34b17fd141e97773","tid":2144849,"uid":74970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:51:56.000Z","msg":"收皮啦淨係識係d左膠到拎光環"},{"pid":"204ba15be19c76815399d73dacb21ae048d37ca1","tid":2144849,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14473c89c01dcca7fec213ba37d9457730a9a1e","tid":2144849,"uid":245409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:39:18.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為講緊last of us 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"6bbb40c7758cbc35d6b3c067907106ae17ada412","tid":2144849,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T18:49:51.000Z","msg":"最新一個po係六月<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XVuxNcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXVuxNcz.jpg&h=c886cba7&s={SIZE}\" />"}}